            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">I have an immediate requirement opening for a <span style="background: yellow">Java Portlet Developer position in Torrance, CA. This is a 3 months contract position</span>. I would appreciate if you could send your updated word format resume along with best contact details ASAP.</font></span></strong></div>
