            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; color: red; font-size: 14pt"><font size="3">Rate&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 55/hr on C2C</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; background: yellow; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Required Qualification:</font></span></strong></div>
            <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Seeking an experienced individual in Java Portlet Development that can code to the JSR 168 and JSR 286. </font></span></strong></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">In addition, we would like this resource to have experience coding to this standard specifically for Liferay. </font></span></strong></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">This will be in the context of coding Java Portlet to Endeca API and modifying existing Java Portlets in Endeca to add Print capabilities and Export to Excel.</font></span></strong></li>
            </ul>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; background: yellow; font-size: 11pt">Required Skills:</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Java - J2EE&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: blue">- 3 years</span></font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt"><font size="3">Java - Java Opensource&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: blue">- 3 years</span></font></span></strong></div>
